snippet.title: Somnium Eleven Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter has launched! And will end on Oct 26th, 2020. Please check it out at and support us at https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/103753487/somnium-eleven?ref=8b0olt

A choice-driven, magitech isekai visual novel (GxB/GXG) featuring in-game social media and an intricate romancing system!
